【完成後削除】このドキュメントで何を「見せたい」か¶

  • 記述統計ができる
    • Descrive
    • 他に何か
  • データの可視化ができる
    • 「情報」を含むデータだけを可視化する
  • 回帰と分類ができる
    • モデルの作成

  • レポート作成ができる

    • LaTexで書き出し。参考文献の体裁をとる

  • その他

    • 学校の差異が学部の差異みたいな

何が「やりたいか・やるべきか」の整理¶

  • G3を説明する変数を探し出す
  • 分かりやすく、情報がまとまったプロットを5種類つぐらい描く 　パイチャート
  • 全体も簡潔にまとめる

データ情報等¶

データ取得元：カリフォルニア大学アーバイン校／機械学習リポジトリ Student Performance Data Set http://archive.ics.uci.edu/ml/datasets/Student+Performance#

関係論文：USING DATA MINING TO PREDICT SECONDARY SCHOOL STUDENT PERFORMANCE http://www3.dsi.uminho.pt/pcortez/student.pdf

https://www.kaggle.com/c/1056lab-student-performance-prediction

urban or 'R' - rural) 5 | famsize | 世帯人数 (binary: 'LE3' - less or equal to 3 or 'GT3' - greater than 3) 6 | Pstatus | 両親との同居有無 (binary: 'T' - living together or 'A' - apart) 7 | Medu | 母親の学歴 (numeric: 0 - none, 1 - primary education (4th grade), 2 - 5th to 9th grade, 3 - secondary education or 4 - higher education) 8 | Fedu | 父親の学歴 (numeric: 0 - none, 1 - primary education (4th grade), 2 - 5th to 9th grade, 3 - secondary education or 4 - higher education) 9 | Mjob | 母親の職業 (nominal: 'teacher', 'health' care related, civil 'services' (e.g. administrative or police), 'at_home' or 'other') 10 | Fjob | 父親の職業 (nominal: 'teacher', 'health' care related, civil 'services' (e.g. administrative or police), 'at_home' or 'other') 11 | reason | 現在の通学校に進学した理由 (nominal: close to 'home', school 'reputation', 'course' preference or 'other') 12 | guardian |　保護者 (nominal: 'mother', 'father' or 'other') 13 |traveltime | 通学時間 (numeric: 1 - In [22]:
def groupmean(d, x, y, z):

  # 受け取ったdfに対してyとzでグループ化
  df_gb = d.groupby([x, y], as_index=False)[z].mean()

  # 出力用dfの外枠作成
  df_out = pd.DataFrame(
    index = df_gb[x].unique(),
    columns= df_gb[y].sort_values().unique())

  # 出力用dfの要素の配置
  for i in range(df_gb.shape[0]):
    v = df_gb.iloc[i]
    df_out.loc[v[0], v[1]] = v[2]
  return df_out

cm = ['Blues', 'Oranges']

# Math or Portuguese
for i in range(2):
  fig, axs = plt.subplots(1, 2, figsize=(12, 5))

  # Dad or Mom
  for j in range(2):
    df_out = groupmean(mp[i], *dm[j])
    sns.heatmap(df_out.fillna(0), mask=df_out.isna(), cmap=cm[j], annot=True, ax=axs[j])
    axs[j].set(title='G3(mean)', xlabel=dm[j][1], ylabel=dm[j][0])
  fig.suptitle(st[i], fontsize=16)
  fig.subplots_adjust(top=.9)
  plt.show()

予測¶

線形回帰¶

In [25]:
# 標準化
def zval(x):
    return (x-x.mean())/x.std(ddof=1)
z = zval(df_m[num])

# onehotベクトル化
w = pd.get_dummies(df_m[cat], drop_first=True)

x = z.join(w)
y = x['G3']
x = x.drop(columns=['G3'])

# データ分割
from sklearn.model_selection import train_test_split
x_train, x_test, y_train, y_test = train_test_split(x, y, test_size=.1, random_state=123)
print(df_m.shape, x_train.shape[0], x_test.shape[0])

# 線形回帰モデル
from sklearn.linear_model import LinearRegression as LR
lr = LR()
lr.fit(x_train, y_train)
y_pred_train = lr.predict(x_train)
y_pred_test = lr.predict(x_test)

# 標準化の逆変換
def zinv(x):
    return x * df_m['G3'].std(ddof=1) + df_m['G3'].mean()

y_pred_train = zinv(y_pred_train)
y_pred_test = zinv(y_pred_test)
y_train = zinv(y_train)
y_test = zinv(y_test)

from sklearn.metrics import mean_squared_error as MSE
rmse_train = np.sqrt(MSE(y_train, y_pred_train))
rmse_test = np.sqrt(MSE(y_test, y_pred_test))
print(round(rmse_train, 2))
print(round(rmse_test, 2))

plt.figure(figsize=(5,5))
plt.scatter(y_pred_test, y_test)
test_max = np.max(y_test)
pred_max = np.max(y_pred_test)
test_min = np.min(y_test)
pred_min = np.min(y_pred_test)
max_value = np.maximum(test_max, pred_max)
min_value = np.minimum(test_min, pred_min)
plt.plot([min_value, max_value],[min_value,max_value])
plt.xlabel('Predictions')
plt.ylabel('True values')
plt.title('Math')
plt.show()

plt.figure(figsize=(20,5))
plt.bar(x=list(x_train.columns), height=lr.coef_)
plt.xticks(rotation=90)
plt.title('Math')
plt.show()

from sklearn.model_selection import train_test_split
x_train, x_test, y_train, y_test = train_test_split(x, y, test_size=.1, random_state=123)
print(df_m.shape, x_train.shape[0], x_test.shape[0])

# ランダムフォレスト
from sklearn.ensemble import RandomForestRegressor
rf = RandomForestRegressor(max_depth=8, random_state=123)
rf.fit(x_train, y_train)
y_pred_train = rf.predict(x_train)
y_pred_test = rf.predict(x_test)

# 標準化の逆変換
def zinv(x):
    return x * df_m['G3'].std(ddof=1) + df_m['G3'].mean()

y_pred_train = zinv(y_pred_train)
y_pred_test = zinv(y_pred_test)
y_train = zinv(y_train)
y_test = zinv(y_test)

from sklearn.metrics import mean_squared_error as MSE
rmse_train = np.sqrt(MSE(y_train, y_pred_train))
rmse_test = np.sqrt(MSE(y_test, y_pred_test))
print(round(rmse_train, 2))
print(round(rmse_test, 2))

plt.figure(figsize=(5,5))
plt.scatter(y_pred_test, y_test)
test_max = np.max(y_test)
test_min = np.min(y_test)
pred_max = np.max(y_pred_test)
pred_min = np.min(y_pred_test)
max_value = np.maximum(test_max, pred_max)
min_value = np.minimum(test_min, pred_min)
plt.plot([min_value, max_value],[min_value,max_value])
plt.xlabel('Predictions')
plt.ylabel('True values')
plt.title('Math')
plt.show()
